title: Exception throws when export data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: Exception throws when attempting to export data from attached report.
OB: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map.
EB: The system should allow users to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map without encountering any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Attempt to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map.
